node.text: I didn’t win the race but my kit was pretty damn cool. Too many mistakes and not enough flow on this run. Time to shine, enough races wasted 💪

node.text:
3rd today ! It was pretty damn hard, different type of track and tight times. Made some mistakes but hats off to @benoitcoulanges for his second title. I need to start being cleaner to get the top spot, that’s the next weeks’ goal. Merci !
📸 @kenoderleyn

node.text: Duuuuur ! First day on the national champs track was touuuugh. Not much flow or grip so it will be hard to not find the limits 😂. Rain has arrived, again...

node.text:
Les Gets never disappoints ! Even though we couldn’t fight for the win, I had an amazing day just thanks to the spectators, I missed you guys so much. Downhill is the best and after this track and crowd, I’m so proud to be French 😍.
🇫🇷 : Les Gets nous a encore fait vibrer !! Dommage pour les conditions mais le public était incroyable, je vous kiffe merci beaucoup ! Fier d’être français. Bravo à @thibautdaprela qui a représenté le pays comme il faut, à l’année prochaine 🙌
📸 Seb Schieck
